execution of =E2=80=9Cjust hand out billions of dollars=E2=80=9D is complic=
ated, but at its core it is a pretty simple business model. The main trick =
is finding someone to give you the billions of dollars.</p><p style=3D"marg=
in: 16px 0;">Last year the U.S. government decided to hand out billions of =
dollars to businesses, in the form of forgivable government-guaranteed loan=
s=C2=A0under the <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/2=
